quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  21,91,"And she, who guarded her private part, then We blew from Our breath/spirit into her, and We made her and her son a sign for humankind"
  21,92,"Indeed this is your community (of faith), a single community and I am your Master so serve Me"
  21,93,"And they cut up their affair (in religion) between them, they all return to Us"
  21,94,"So anyone who does from the good works and is a believer, then there is no rejection for his efforts and We are writers for him"
  21,95,"And it is forbidden for (people of) a town that We destroyed it (to return), indeed they do not return"
  21,96,"until when (the barrier of) Ya’juj and Ma’juj (Gog and Magog) is opened, and they rush out from every hill"
  21,97,"And the true promise got close, then when the eyes of those who disbelieved gaze (they say): woe to us, we were definitely ignorant of this, rather we were wrongdoers"
  21,98,"(They will be told): indeed you and what you serve other than God are fuel for hell, and you will arrive (in it)"
  21,99,"If these were (true) gods, they would not have arrived in it, and all of you remain in it forever"
  21,100,They have moaning (and groaning) in it and they do not hear (anything) in it
  21,101,"Indeed those whom the good (reward) came from Us for them previously (due to their belief and good deeds), they are removed far from it"